OL,3,CMark Drakeford delivers emotional
OL,4,Cfinal speech as FM after 'saddest' 12
OL,5,Cmonths
OL,7,FHe said: "I will be very glad to get
OL,8,Fmy weekends back and not to spend
OL,9,FTuesday mornings in the mad dash for
OL,10,FFMQs."
OL,12,FAs for whether he will be vocal from
OL,13,Fthe backbenches, he said: "I think the
OL,14,Fpeople deserve a short period of
OL,15,Fsilence, as they say, I don't think
OL,16,FI'll be dashing to do it straight away
OL,17,Fbut there are two years to go."
